  "description": "Welcome to Casa Cielo! Casa Cielo is a beautifully presented 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartment in Aldea Blanca, offering modern comfort in one of Nueva Andalucía’s most sought-after gated communities. The apartment features a bright open-plan layout where the living, dining, and kitchen areas flow seamlessly together, creating a spacious and sociable environment filled with natural light. Large sliding glass doors connect the interior directly to the terrace, enhancing the airy feel throughout. One of the bedrooms blends effortlessly into the living area, creating a flexible space that can function as an additional lounge-style room or guest area while maintaining the apartment’s open, contemporary aesthetic. Warm wooden flooring and neutral tones give the home a calm, modern atmosphere.\n\nThe generous private terrace is a true highlight, offering beautiful sunset and sea views from its elevated position. With both dining and lounge areas, it provides the perfect setting for relaxed evenings and outdoor entertaining. Aldea Blanca is known for its lush landscaped gardens and exceptionally well-maintained communal pool areas, creating a peaceful oasis within a secure gated complex. Ideally located, the apartment is within easy walking distance to Puerto Banús, shops, restaurants and the beach, offering both convenience and lifestyle in equal measure. Please note, the building does not have an elevator.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.",
